        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Strengthening Social Security For Widows Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases Social Security benefits for widows or widowers in two-income households by establishing an alternative method to calculate survivors benefits based on combined household benefit amounts. It also allows disabled widows and widowers to receive benefits before age 50.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
